snippet.title: Buzz!™: The Ultimate Music Quiz
snippet.description: Get your finger on the buzzer because it's time to face the music in the quiz show that makes you the star. With Buzz! The Ultimate Music Quiz, music lovers and quiz fans will find endless fun with their family and friends. Tackle thousands of music trivia questions in rounds like Tune Warp, Pie Fight! and Watch It!; challenge up to 8 friends at the same time and take quizzing into a new dimension with four new rounds designed specifically for PlayStation®Move.
